---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<Layout
  title="About APA Maritime"
  description="Learn about APA Maritime's 25+ years of experience in maritime logistics and shipping solutions."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section
    class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
  >
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <Image
        src="/images/about.jpeg"
        alt="About APA Maritime"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        width={1920}
        height={1080}
        loading="eager"
      />
      <!-- Dark overlay for better text readability -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary opacity-60"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="container-custom relative z-10 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-slide-up">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          About APA Maritime
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-100">
          With over 75 years of industry expertise, we've established ourselves
          as a trusted leader in maritime logistics and shipping solutions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-10 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <!-- Intro Section -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center animate-slide-up">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          At APA Maritime, we don't just facilitate shipments and execute
          projects, we deliver reliability, efficiency, and innovation across
          the world's oceans. As a premier maritime solutions provider, APA
          Maritime is dedicated to offering comprehensive and integrated
          services across the global shipping value chain. Our mission is to
          empower clients with strategic advantages, commercial leverage,
          operational efficiency, and sustainable growth in an increasingly
          dynamic and complex industry.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Three Pillars Section -->
      <div class="mt-8">
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-primary mb-8 animate-slide-up"
        >
          This mission is built on three core pillars
        </h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Pillar 1 -->
          <div
            class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 hover:bg-primary hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2 animate-slide-up"
            style="animation-delay: 0.1s"
          >
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary group-hover:bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors duration-500"
            >
              <svg
                class="pillar-icon w-8 h-8 text-white transition-colors duration-500"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4
              class="text-xl font-bold text-primary group-hover:text-white mb-4 transition-colors duration-500"
            >
              Expert Chartering & Operations
            </h4>
            <p
              class="text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-100 transition-colors duration-500"
            >
              Specialist commercial and operational management of bulk carriers,
              oil tankers, chemical and edible-oil tankers, and gas carriers.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Pillar 2 -->
          <div
            class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 hover:bg-primary hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2 animate-slide-up"
            style="animation-delay: 0.2s"
          >
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary group-hover:bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors duration-500"
            >
              <svg
                class="pillar-icon w-8 h-8 text-white transition-colors duration-500"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M17 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm7-5a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4
              class="text-xl font-bold text-primary group-hover:text-white mb-4 transition-colors duration-500"
            >
              Tailored Shipbroking Services
            </h4>
            <p
              class="text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-100 transition-colors duration-500"
            >
              Bespoke spot, time, S&P and demolition broking solutions designed
              around the diverse needs of charterers, owners, traders, and
              operators.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Pillar 3 -->
          <div
            class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 hover:bg-primary hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2 animate-slide-up"
            style="animation-delay: 0.3s"
          >
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary group-hover:bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors duration-500"
            >
              <svg
                class="pillar-icon w-8 h-8 text-white transition-colors duration-500"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4
              class="text-xl font-bold text-primary group-hover:text-white mb-4 transition-colors duration-500"
            >
              Maritime Consulting & Service Solutions
            </h4>
            <p
              class="text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-100 transition-colors duration-500"
            >
              A robust portfolio of advisory and operational support services
              providing strategic insights, data-driven analysis, and practical
              solutions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Closing Statement -->
      <div
        class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-light rounded-2xl p-10 text-white text-center animate-slide-up"
        style="animation-delay: 0.4s"
      >
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          In an era defined by market volatility, evolving environmental
          regulations, and rapid technological change, APA Maritime stands out
          through deep domain expertise, an integrated service model and
          proactive market intelligence, ensuring our clients stay ahead in
          every decision they make. The company's unique value proposition
          extends far beyond facilitating transactions. APA Maritime delivers
          end-to-end strategic guidance that helps clients mitigate risks,
          optimise performance, and adopt future-ready solutions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

